- if users.any?
  %h2 Teamless users
  %p Following users are not assigned to any team on GitHub. You should probably remove them.
  %table.table
    %thead
      %tr
        %th Name
        %th Github handle
        %th Email
    %tbody
      - users.each do |u|
        %tr
          %td
            = u.name
          %td
            = link_to u.github, u.html_url
          %td
            = u.email
- else
  %h2 Teamless users
  %p There are no users without a team on GitHub. Great job!

